## 1. Introduction

### 1.1 Purpose

This test plan defines the testing strategy, scope, schedule, and resources for the **Injector** module (KSA-3) of the Kiro SDLC Agent VS Code extension.

### 1.2 Test Objectives

* Verify all five functional features work per FSD specifications
* Validate all 17 business rules (BR-1 through BR-17)
* Ensure directory exclusion logic is case-sensitive and applies at any depth
* Verify cross-platform path handling
* Confirm error handling produces correct messages per FSD Section 9
* Validate non-functional requirements (performance ≤ 5s, async I/O)

