## 7. Risk & Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Cross-platform path differences | High | Test on all 3 OS in CI |
| Mock-fs inaccuracy | Medium | Supplement with real-fs IT |
| VS Code test harness instability | Medium | Pin version; retry flaky |

## 8. Defect Management

| Severity | Definition |
| --- | --- |
| Critical | Core copy logic broken, data loss |
